OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,FFormer Lioness Mary Earps has
OL,7,Fapologised for the "hurt" her
OL,8,Fcontroversial book release caused and
OL,9,Ftold ITV News things got "out of
OL,10,Fcontrol".
OL,12,FHer autobiography caused a huge stir
OL,13,Fin November when extracts highlighted
OL,14,Fher relationship with England boss
OL,15,FSarina Wiegman and fellow goalkeeper
OL,16,FHannah Hampton.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,FIn an exclusive TV interview, she told
OL,7,FITV News Central: "I've reached out to
OL,8,Fpeople involved and taken
OL,9,Faccountability and apologised for the
OL,10,Fhurt and the impact that the book
OL,11,Fwould have had on them and people
OL,12,Faround them.
OL,14,F"I think the big conversation really
OL,15,Fthat was important to me was with
OL,16,FSarina, we had an opportunity to meet
OL,17,Fface to face and have a conversation.
OL,19,F"It was a really positive
OL,20,Fconversation. I'm really grateful that
OL,21,Fwe were able to do that in person."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,FEarps wrote in her autobiography that
OL,7,Fshe told Wiegman that she was
OL,8,F'rewarding bad behaviour' by selecting
OL,9,FHampton.
OL,11,FThe 32-year-old retired from
OL,12,Finternational football ahead of last
OL,13,Fyear's Euros but is still playing club
OL,14,Ffootball for Paris Saint-Germain. It
OL,15,Fis very rare for current players to
OL,16,Fwrite about conversations with those
OL,17,Fstill in football.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,FWhen the book was released in
OL,7,FNovember, Earps followed it up with a
OL,8,Fseries of what she now sees as
OL,9,F"defensive" interviews.
OL,11,FShe said her family "held up a mirror"
OL,12,Fto her and she is now more calm.
OL,14,FShe said: "It's been a crazy, crazy
OL,15,Ftime. Especially November and December
OL,16,Fwas pretty difficult.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,F"The way I describe it is it's like my
OL,7,Ffirst experience of cancel culture and
OL,8,FI wouldn't recommend it to people.
OL,9,FJokes aside, November, December were
OL,10,Ftough, but ultimately it's off the
OL,11,Fback of my book, which is my name, my
OL,12,Fface and I take full accountability
OL,13,Ffor that.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,F"It wasn't necessarily about the fact
OL,7,Fthat I shared my experiences, it was
OL,8,Fmore in the way that some of it was
OL,9,Fexpressed. The way I articulated
OL,10,Fmyself at times, decisions made around
OL,11,Fthe book as well. Not just the book
OL,12,Fitself. So, yeah, there's a bunch of
OL,13,Fthings.
OL,15,F"It kind of went out of control really
OL,16,Fquickly. I think all you can do from
OL,17,Fthat point is learn and grow. I take
OL,18,Fmy responsibility as a role model
OL,19,Freally seriously.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,F"You can't just be maybe front and
OL,7,Fcentre and follow the joys of spring
OL,8,Fwhen things are really good. Of course
OL,9,Flife brings tough lessons sometimes, I
OL,10,Fthink it's important to be authentic
OL,11,Fand accountable in those moments as
OL,12,Fwell. I think that's what true role
OL,13,Fmodels should be.
OL,15,F"They should be able to take
OL,16,Fresponsibility when things don't quite
OL,17,Fgo to plan, or when there are things
OL,18,Fthat they could have done better in
OL,19,Fthe situation, and that they've
OL,20,Flearned lessons from."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,FIn 2024, Earps was named the best
OL,7,Fgoalkeeper in the world for the second
OL,8,Fyear running. She helped England win
OL,9,Fthe Euros in 2022 and saved a penalty
OL,10,Fin the World Cup final a year later.
OL,12,FShe retired ahead of last summer's
OL,13,FEuros when it became clear that
OL,14,FHampton was first choice.
OL,16,FEarps told ITV News Central: "I wrote
OL,17,Fthis book at a really emotional point
OL,18,Fin my life. The emotions were running
OL,19,Freally high.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,F"In my head it made perfect sense to
OL,7,Fkind of then go from there and dive
OL,8,Fheadfirst into into a book that, you
OL,9,Fknow, I thought I would share my
OL,10,Fexperiences and it would help people."
OL,12,FShe adds: "But ultimately the impact
OL,13,Fthat the book had, it went in a
OL,14,Fcertain direction. I think that,
OL,15,Fsometimes that's where intention
OL,16,Fdoesn't matter.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,F"You know, you have to look at the
OL,7,Fimpact and, yeah, I think it was
OL,8,Freally ambitious to write a book
OL,9,Fwhilst I was still playing, I think I
OL,10,Fknew that it would be a risk at the
OL,11,Ftime anyway.
OL,13,F"I think being more removed and being
OL,14,Fin a place where I've been able to
OL,15,Freflect and really have some tough
OL,16,Fconversations, really lean on my
OL,17,Ffriends and family where they've held
OL,18,Fthe mirror up to me at times, but
OL,19,Fwhere they've also picked me up when
OL,20,FI've needed it at times.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772021934
OL,3,CMary Earps: 'I'm sorry for the hurt my
OL,4,Cbook caused'
OL,6,F"Now I can understand the reaction of
OL,7,Fcertain parts, and now I can see why
OL,8,Fpeople saw things a certain way."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
